{
    "advancement.takumicraft.creeperbarrel.desc": "引爆苦力怕大桶爆弹G\n\n看起来像是\n什么很危險的东西啊。\n如果把什么會爆炸的东西\n放進去的话會發生什么呢。\n爆炸就是藝術！",
    "advancement.takumicraft.creeperbarrel.title": "接受G的洗礼吧",
    "advancement.takumicraft.creeperbomb.desc": "获得一顆苦力怕炸弹\n一切都要从炸弹说起。",
    "advancement.takumicraft.creeperbomb.title": "小心爆炸",
    "advancement.takumicraft.creepercampfire.desc": "在防爆苦力怕营火處休息\n\n展現爆炸吧。如果还有可以回去的地方的话。",
    "advancement.takumicraft.creepercampfire.title": "CAMPFIRE LIT",
    "advancement.takumicraft.creepershield.desc": "获得一張苦力怕盾\n⋯⋯就是卖相不咋樣。",
    "advancement.takumicraft.creepershield.title": "爆炸不是事儿！",
    "advancement.takumicraft.disarmament.desc": "解除巨大苦力怕状態\n無所畏惧，苦力怕的猎手。",
    "advancement.takumicraft.disarmament.title": "武裝解除",
    "advancement.takumicraft.kingslayer.desc": "打倒帝王苦力怕\n\n物語は、ほんの始まり。\n次の世界の扉が開かれる刻を待て。",
    "advancement.takumicraft.kingslayer.title": "帝王=杀手",
    "advancement.takumicraft.rainbowsheep.desc": "杀死彩虹羊苦力怕\n\n也许能帶来好運⋯⋯？",
    "advancement.takumicraft.rainbowsheep.title": "绚丽彩虹",
    "advancement.takumicraft.root.desc": "歡迎来到苦力怕的混沌世界！\n接受爆炸的洗礼吧。",
    "advancement.takumicraft.root.title": "苦力怕世界",
    "advancement.takumicraft.slay_all.desc": "完成苦力怕圖鑑\n靜待王的新造物吧。",
    "advancement.takumicraft.slay_all.title": "完全統治",
    "advancement.takumicraft.spmeat.desc": "品尝過所有的苦力怕特級肉\n\n肉！！\n太好吃了吧！！\n給我反省啊！！",
    "advancement.takumicraft.spmeat.title": "苦力怕认證特級肉",
